    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This car is in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience that you're sure to love. While it shows the typical character of a well-loved vehicle, it remains clean, dependable, and ready for many more miles of adventure. It's the perfect balance of quality and value for anyone looking for a great ride!",
