    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of life left? This car is a fantastic opportunity for someone who values character and reliability! It\u2019s in fair condition, showing some honest wear from its time on the road, but it still runs strong and is ready for its next adventure. It\u2019s a great, budget-friendly option that gets the job done with a smile!",
