      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for those seeking functional transportation on a budget. The engine starts reliably and the transmission shifts through all gears, though you may notice some typical mechanical noise consistent with its age. The exterior shows its history with several noticeable scratches, minor dings on the passenger side, and some fading paint on the hood. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays clear signs of use, including some wear on the driver's seat upholstery and a few non-essential interior trim pieces that are loose. It is a solid, honest car that has been maintained to stay roadworthy, though it is not a showpiece.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Maintained to rigorous standards, it offers a seamless blend of performance and long-term reliability. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust mechanical profile, this unit stands as a testament to quality engineering. We invite you to experience the refined handling and sophisticated presence of this professionally vetted automobile.",
